title: Michelle Buteau
description: Michelle Buteau (Comedy Central! VH1! Last Comic Standing!) is a wonderful, wonderful weirdo and just a true delight! DARE I SAY SASSY?! I dare. So much sassitude. SASSITUDE. So much fun. Please enjoy this romp down comedy, friendship, and fun. GET INTO IT YOU WEIRDOS!!
